track_notes: The entrance to the chapel car park off the A595 at Whicham is easily missed. A path at the rear of the church takes you up to Black Combe.
track_title: Black Combe one way from Whicham

track_notes: Using two cars - one parked in layby at Fox and Goose Cottages, the other on CP at Whicham Church. Climb to White Combe LDO-044, Stoupdale crags LDO-034 and then proceed to Black Combe LD-030.
track_title: Linear walk Black Combe + 2 Wainwright Outlyers
